Dear St Joseph of Cupertino, you were an unwanted child and were thought worthless even by your own mother. Intercede for all unwanted children that they may come to know they were born out of God‚Äôs love for them. We pray especially for

(mention request here‚Ä¶) Our Father Hail Mary Glory Be St. Joseph of Cupertino, pray for us!

